==== ENTRY 1 ====
HEADWORD: Minie ball
<hw>Min"ie ball`</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>. <ety>[From the inventor, Captain
<ets>Mini⟦eacute⟧</ets>, of France.]</ety> <def>A conical rifle bullet,
with a cavity in its base plugged with a piece of iron, which, by the
explosion of the charge, is driven farther in, expanding the sides to
fit closely the grooves of the barrel.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

<p><ent>Minie rifle</ent>⟦br⟧
